	^ HelpTopic
		title: 'General Switch Information'
		contents: (EpicHelp showHTML: 
'<h1>General Switch Information</h1>

<p>A switch is a component that outputs a specific value, which could be simply a constant value, or based on for example user input or time.</p>

<p>To use a switch simply drag and drop it into your circuit and connect the output ports with other components.</p>')